  in 2005 , colgate sold the under - performing brands fab , dynamo , arctic power , abc , cold power and fresh start , as well as the license of the ajax brand for laundry detergents in the us , canada and puerto rico , to phoenix brands , llc as part of their plan to focus on their higher margin oral , personal , and pet care products .

